<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/47332603-cully"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/47332603-cully">Cully</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Some of this gets explained in depth in the third section of the second omnibus which covers the fall of Silo 17. The power for the grow lights is bei<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Some of this gets explained in depth in the third section of the second omnibus which covers the fall of Silo 17. The power for the grow lights is being stolen from the hidden IT level where Solo spent the first 15 or 20 years after the collapse of the silo. Similar to where Lucas was held. That section has its own power supply that is actually provided by Silo 1 rather than the Mechanical sections that provide power to the rest of the silo. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
