<div id="review_2195431485" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2195431485" />
    <a title="Dannii Elle" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/44487975-dannii-elle"><img alt="Dannii Elle" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1623521403p2/44487975.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2195431485?book_show_action=true">Dec 03, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dannii Elle" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dannii Elle" href="/user/show/44487975-dannii-elle">Dannii Elle</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780099580485" href="/book/show/17307614-wool">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44487975-dannii-elle?shelf=science-fiction-sagacity">science-fiction-sagacity</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44487975-dannii-elle?shelf=adult-books-read">adult-books-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/44487975-dannii-elle?shelf=satirical-susceptiveness">satirical-susceptiveness</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2195431485" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10571317182122943388">Wool is such a fascinating and absorbing political sci-fi. Give me the most complex of high fantasy worlds or magic systems and I can navigate them with no problem, but for some reason science fiction can sometimes completely baffle me. Not so here, thankfully! I was completely captivated with this early dystopian novel and chilling insight to the possible future of humanity.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


